OL,3,CInvestigation into Wincanton flat fire
OL,4,Cin which man died
OL,6,FAn investigation has started into the
OL,7,Fdeath of a man in a flat fire in
OL,8,FWincanton.
OL,10,FFire crews were alerted during the
OL,11,Fearly hours of this morning (March 4)
OL,12,Fafter the blaze was reported at
OL,13,FFairfield Court.
OL,15,FThe flat was completely destroyed and
OL,16,Fthere was smoke damage to a number of
OL,17,Fadjoining flats.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
