OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772716281
OL,3,CInvestigation into Wincanton flat fire
OL,4,Cin which man died
OL,6,FCrews from Yeovil, Castle Cary and
OL,7,FWincanton were first on the scene just
OL,8,Fafter 1.30am and, given the severity
OL,9,Fof the blaze, asked for an aerial
OL,10,Fladder and an additional fire engine.
OL,12,FDevon and Somerset Fire and Rescue
OL,13,FService confirmed the cause of the
OL,14,Ffire was under investigation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
