PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772716281
OL,3,CInvestigation into Wincanton flat fire
OL,4,Cin which man died
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Avon and Somerset
OL,7,FPolice said: "Sadly, one person was
OL,8,Fpronounced deceased at the scene.
OL,9,FAlthough formal identification has yet
OL,10,Fto take place, the family of a man
OL,11,Fhave been informed and our thoughts
OL,12,Fare with them.
OL,14,F"We are working alongside fire service
OL,15,Finvestigators as part of their work to
OL,16,Fidentify the cause of the fire."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
